description:
Badge component references --color-destructive-foreground but it doesn't exist in theme.css.

## Impact
- Badge destructive variant falls back to inherited text color
- Potential WCAG contrast failure

## Fix
Add to theme.css:
```css
:root {
  --destructive-foreground: oklch(0.985 0.002 247.839);
}

.dark {
  --destructive-foreground: oklch(0.13 0.028 261.692);
}
```

Also add to @theme inline block:
```css
--color-destructive-foreground: var(--destructive-foreground);
```

